{"tid":981050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加拿大薑汁汽水廠商認了「不含薑汁」 將賠錢給消費者","createTime":"2019-01-14T03:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T11:23:51.000Z","uid":32511,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c943267abeb1d5a4e9865cbbdd971c1d5bcddf0b","tid":981050,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:31:12.000Z","msg":"加拿大媒體《國家郵報》（National Post）報導，加拿大薑汁汽水（Canada Dryginger ale）面對廣告不實訴訟案，不打算打官司，將不再聲稱「提煉自真薑」，這是在<br />\n美國遭遇多起集體訴訟案和解條件的其中一部分。<br />\n <br />\n生產製造廣受歡迎的加拿大薑汁汽水的Keurig Dr. Pepper公司，也提議賠償自2013年以來購買薑汁汽水自用的美國消費者。沒有購買證明的家庭最高賠償5.2美元（約台幣162元），有購買證明的家庭賠償上限為40美元（約台幣1243元），但賠償事宜不適用於加拿大或國際市場的銷售。<br />\n <br />\n根據Keurig Dr. Pepper的委任律師，該公司正試圖通知任何可能符合賠償資格的消費者，希望最終能在4月獲法院核准該和解案。"},{"pid":"e9c0b1628e64c3cb3152dc3ae4f2e7546d5f01db","tid":981050,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61157d6020a91949f2ce1e0e98cc0171b9742245","tid":981050,"uid":6845,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:32:29.000Z","msg":"沒有購買證明都有得賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063ae7abc7af640fda709829408189c6f8b53133","tid":981050,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df55f57c029d436b7425b039401860f88c285393","tid":981050,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:05:54.000Z","msg":"只能叫「薑汁<span style=\"color: red;\">味</span>汽水」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bf06bbb176ea34ed85ef9722d86f86e4afe8fd","tid":981050,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T04:07:16.000Z","msg":"m記新地都唔敢自稱雪糕"},{"pid":"7c72509a6e3a06d81192a5d1302b0c7abae7efa9","ti